\Phi(t+\delta t)=2\Phi(t)-\Phi(t-\delta t)+\delta t^{2}\omega^{2}\left(\Psi^{\mathrm{sc}}(t)-\Phi(t)\right)+\alpha\sum_{m-0}^{K}c_{m}\Phi(t-m\delta t)
